Name: Average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average waiting time to SW-AE Assign Reviewers following SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants that include SW-Reviewer No Response
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer No Response'

Name: Time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in cases where at least one reviewer agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the subsequent occurrence of Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Minimum time between SW-AE Assign Reviewers and SW-Reviewer Unavailable
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Unavailable'

Name: Total time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers to result in a completed reviewer assignment (i.e., followed by SW-Reviewer Agreed without subsequent decline)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time from SW-Initial Reviewer Selection to SW-AE Assign Reviewers compared to the average time from SW-AE Assign Reviewers to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time of SW-AE Assign Reviewers in variants that involve multiple reassignments versus variants with a single assignment
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity SW-AE Assign Reviewers and the end of the case

Name: Total time between consecutive occurrences of SW-AE Assign Reviewers within the same case until SW-Reviewer Agreed is reached
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers after SW-Reviewer Selection is now due to produce SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Average time for SW-AE Assign Reviewers grouped by case:concept:name in variants leading to SW-EIC Major Revision
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'
